## XUIFramwork

### Recycler adapters - wiki >
pre-made common types of recycler adapters, like pagination adapter, multiselection adapter, etc. 
### Custom views - wiki >
extended android views to use them easily or use custom fonts, such as easy spinner, image pickers, expandable layout, etc.
### Form - wiki >
easily create forms:

`Form.with(activity, yourLinearLayoutOrViewGroup).editText("text 1").row().checkbox("check box").finish()`
### Auto Form - wiki >
create forms using entity models and annotations:

`data class Person(@Input(displayName = "name hint") var name: String)`
### Data - wiki >
access android shared prefrences, create easy http requests and get result as raw text, JSONObject or data model.
### Custom dialogs - wiki >
info, ask and input dialog
### Other code utils - wiki >
